title: Quick Draw Complete Season 1 and Webisode Specials
description:
s01e01 Murder at the Webb Ranch
Sheriff John Henry Hoyle attempts to use his state-of-the-art forensics training from Harvard to solve a rancher's murder.

s01e02 The Legend of Belle Starr
Hoyle's old friend from Harvard, Xavier (Robert Cuthill) arrives in town to open a new bank. After Frank James attempts to rob the bank, Hoyle and Eli apprehend Frank's girlfriend, Pearl Starr (Alexia Dox), who just might have a secret link to Hoyle's past.

s01e03 Mail Order Bride
A mail order bride comes to Great Bend.

s01e04 Expert Witness
Sheriff John Henry Hoyle is an expert witness.

s01e05 Temperance
Sheriff John Henry Hoyle weighs competing interests.

s01e06 Nicodemus
Sheriff John Henry Hoyle visits a nearby town.

s01e07 Honey's Beau
Sheriff John Henry Hoyle fights a duel.

s01e08 The Railroad Spur
Sheriff Hoyle and Eli use trigonometry to determine that murderers where on Mayor Dodge's property. Hoyle, Eli, Mayor Dodge, and school teacher, Mr. Tidwell, stand in for Prostitue/Hoyle's step-daughter, Pearl, as Honey's girls'
